  FlowForge Orchestrator: @ConfigurationPropertiesScan(\"com.flowforge\") so MlflowProperties
                          is bound alongside FlowForgeProperties.

3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  MlflowClient:        @Component using Spring RestClient; getOrCreateExperiment(name) calls
                       /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/get-by-name with fallback to /experiments/create,
                       parses JSON via ObjectMapper to return experiment_id; createRun(experimentId, runName, tags)
                       posts to /runs/create, parses run.info.run_id; logParam, logMetric, logBatch post to
                       corresponding MLflow endpoints; logArtifact PUTs to /mlflow-artifacts with octet-stream.
  ExperimentTracker:   @Service; trackRun(runName, params, TrainingFunction<T>) resolves experiment,
                       creates run with tags (mlflow.source.name=flowforge, mlflow.runName, java.version),
                       logs params via logBatch, executes training function with TrainingContext(runId, tracker),
                       and ends run with FINISHED or FAILED; TrainingContext helpers logMetric, logArtifact(Object),
                       logModel(byte[]).
  MlflowHealthIndicator: @Component HealthIndicator; calls /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search?max_results=1 on
                         trackingUri; reports Health.up with trackingUri on success, Health.down with detail on error.
  TrackedAnomalyTrainer: libs/anomaly @Service; wraps AnomalyDetectorModel training with ExperimentTracker,
                         logging snapshot_id, model_type, num_trees, subsample_size, feature_count, feature_dim,
                         metric training_samples, and model artifact models/anomaly-model.smile.
  TrackedGnnTrainer:    libs/gnn @Component; wraps GnnInferenceService.predictLinks/classifyNodes with ExperimentTracker,
                         logging num_nodes, num_edges, link_threshold and metrics predicted_links, classified_nodes.

4. UNIT TESTS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  MlflowClientTest:        WireMock-based; verifies getOrCreateExperiment existing/404→create, createRun returns runId,
                           logParam/logMetric payloads, logArtifact PUT with octet-stream, endRun FINISHED status.
  ExperimentTrackerTest:   Mocks MlflowClient; ensures trackRun logs params via logBatch, ends run FINISHED on success
                           and FAILED on exception.
  MlflowHealthIndicatorTest: WireMock-based; reports Status.UP when search endpoint responds 200, Status.DOWN on 5xx.
  TrackedAnomalyTrainerTest: Mocks ExperimentTracker; verifies trainTracked(\"snap-1\", ...) calls tracker.trackRun
                             with run name anomaly-snap-1 and parameter map including model_type.
  TrackedGnnTrainerTest:   Mocks GnnInferenceService and ExperimentTracker; verifies runTracked delegates to
